        <div class="w-1 bg-indigo-100 rounded shrink-0 mt-1"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap mb-1">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Amazon</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-indigo-600">SDE2 — Route53 & DNS Infrastructure</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 shrink-0">Sep 2024 – Present · Herndon, US</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Working on Route53 DNS infrastructure and Route53 QueryLogging components</li>
            <li>Large-scale data processing of DNS query data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-1 bg-indigo-100 rounded shrink-0 mt-1"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap mb-1">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Amazon</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-indigo-600">SDE2 — Amazon Music</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 shrink-0">Nov 2022 – Aug 2024 · Bangalore</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Promoted Amazon Music app installs via Amazon Retail Music through In-App message campaigns and experiments</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-1 bg-indigo-100 rounded shrink-0 mt-1"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap mb-1">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Udaan</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-indigo-600">Software Engineer — Financial Platform</p>
