            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 shrink-0">Jul 2020 – Nov 2020 · Bangalore</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Built deep-learning based demand & price forecasting time series models and model inference services</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-1 bg-indigo-100 rounded shrink-0 mt-1"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap mb-1">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Capillary Technologies</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-indigo-600">Machine Learning Engineer</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 shrink-0">May 2018 – Apr 2020 · Bangalore</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
